{"tid":2503943,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"好嫲嫲擬買三房方便孫女上學 晉環超額認購逾10倍","createTime":"2021-04-25T12:54:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T09:42:51.000Z","uid":99885,"like":43,"dislike":74,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"0e213140c3fe34b6efc5d4a86e0fd861fed16e16","tid":2503943,"uid":99885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T12:54:13.000Z","msg":"鐵路新盤具競爭力，路勁地產銷售及市場推廣總監封海倫今日(25日)表示，旗下合作發展的香港仔黃竹坑站晉環截至下午3時共收錄逾1,700張入票，較項目首張推出160伙超額認購逾10倍。因應市場反應熱烈，將與合作發展伙伴商討後，最快在2至3日內加推單位，初步料加推最少80個單位，甚或是同時公布銷售安排，惟其後不排除有加價空間⋯<br />\n<br />\n現居於西半山的參觀人士郭太表示，由於孫女在香港大學上學，較對今次新盤感興趣，認為該盤鄰近地鐵站交通方便，又可以方便孫女上學，今次參選主要是「幫吓眼」，最終是否入票仍由兒子決定。她暫有意選購三房單位，惟認為該盤首張價單的29,689港元折實平均呎價頗貴，驚訝疫情下樓價仍然進取<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmV4wfz4VYhGYHN9xRrcwdpKtztvaf3UepETqyx2mPtVjw?filename=NrT4AsE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNrT4AsE.jpg&h=7bd1d98c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"618e9e2f4967b84f7cb51ff73f2b261e8a1efbcd","tid":2503943,"uid":38904,"like":103,"dislike":2,"score":101,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T12:55:39.000Z","msg":"我唔努力了<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/scratching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7410242a14733489d9cb509300bbb214b01aa289","tid":2503943,"uid":344567,"like":450,"dislike":2,"score":448,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T12:56:07.000Z","msg":"嫲嫲你仲有個乖孫喺度呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ec4c0fdba9e0852581782a793f47f90bbb0132","tid":2503943,"uid":103759,"like":173,"dislike":1,"score":172,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T12:58:21.000Z","msg":"嫲嫲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係你失散多年嘅乖孫吖"},{"pid":"da77502abcf58d24